WEBVTT

00:01.920 --> 00:03.120
If we can recover the imperial seal

00:03.480 --> 00:03.920
For us

00:04.520 --> 00:05.520
It would be heaven's mercy

00:05.960 --> 00:07.000
But fortune and misfortune are intertwined

00:07.800 --> 00:09.480
This seal is also a hot potato

00:10.000 --> 00:11.120
The longer we stay in Yiyang

00:11.400 --> 00:12.200
The more likely things will change

00:13.160 --> 00:13.880
Once we get the seal

00:14.280 --> 00:15.160
Seal the news immediately

00:15.480 --> 00:16.240
We'll claim illness

00:16.720 --> 00:17.240
And return south quickly

00:18.240 --> 00:18.760
Yes

00:20.720 --> 00:21.240
Come, come

00:21.560 --> 00:22.680
Today Prince of Jin is hosting a banquet

00:23.160 --> 00:24.200
Everyone gets to enjoy it too

00:25.000 --> 00:25.480
Brothers

00:25.800 --> 00:26.040
Come

00:26.520 --> 00:26.960
Have a drink, have a drink

00:36.280 --> 00:37.040
Drinking at this time

00:37.560 --> 00:38.720
Gives us some benefit

00:39.000 --> 00:39.920
Boosts morale

00:40.720 --> 00:41.680
Don't worry about what the higher-ups think

00:41.960 --> 00:42.920
This wine is the real deal

00:43.880 --> 00:45.120
Come, come

00:46.920 --> 00:47.280
Come, bottoms up

00:47.480 --> 00:47.800
Come, bottoms up

00:47.800 --> 00:48.160
Bottoms up

00:48.200 --> 00:48.640
Bottoms up

00:49.640 --> 00:50.360
Everyone, keep drinking

00:50.600 --> 00:52.000
I'll send some to the other brothers too

00:57.560 --> 00:58.360
At the banquet

00:58.920 --> 01:01.160
You toast back and forth with Chu Maolun

01:01.960 --> 01:02.920
After three rounds

01:03.360 --> 01:05.280
Chu Maolun urgently goes to relieve himself

01:05.720 --> 01:07.360
But even the soldiers guarding him

01:07.480 --> 01:08.680
Disappear together

01:09.000 --> 01:12.080
Just as you're lost in fantasies about the seal

01:12.240 --> 01:15.680
The city gates are opened by traitors under cover of night
